                    <div><p>First, I would like to thank you for all you do and continue to do on behalf of Miner National Service.  Lately, it has become very clear that our current process for collecting and remitting payment is not working and we are causing harm to our relationship with our most valuable commodity, our Affiliates. </p></div>
                   
